review_blob: Had one of these before Super Bowl. None of the nasty aftertaste of other brews of the hood, like OE 800HG or Steel Reserve. Unfortunately, did not have the buzz factor of those two malts
By far the best of the ghetto high gravities (St. Ides OE 800 HG) Much better than the silver can Steel Reserve. At $0.99 for 24 oz. a price performer
